" Multiple windows {
  " One full screen window and closed other windows displayed at the edges of
  " the screen
  nmap <C-J> <C-W>j<C-W>_
  nmap <C-K> <C-W>k<C-W>_
  nmap <C-H> <C-W>h<C-W>_
  nmap <C-L> <C-W>l<C-W>_
" }

" Git shortcuts {
" }
